Jade Global Holdings, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 2:20 PM ET
Specialty Retail

Company Overview of Jade Global Holdings, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Jade Global Holdings, Inc. does not have significant operations. The company intends to engage in the wholesale and retail trade of jade and jade products through retail stores and online Website. The company was formerly known as Media Analytics Corporation and changed its name Jade Global Holdings, Inc. to in January 2017. Jade Global Holdings, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in Coral Gables, Florida.


1825 Ponce de Leon BoulevardSuite 411Coral Gables, FL 33134United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 786-323-7900

jadeglobalholdings.com







