Media Analytics 

 
Comprehensive analytics to provide visibility into online video quality and audience behavior 


Media Analytics is a self-serve SaaS solution designed to provide actionable and relevant reports that help support strategic decision-making. Our wide array of metrics and dashboards give you as much flexibility and granularity as you need for insights into your online media workflow.
Gain an intimate understanding of your online video performance and audience experience through uncovering key insights that help drive your business goals. Our four modules are fully integrated with Akamai’s media delivery solutions and many online video players: Quality of Service Monitor, Viewer Diagnostics, Media Analytics and Download Analytics.


